I support my neighborhood not crooks.

originalText.text: Nelson is awesome! Was on a hunt today for a barber since my regular guy was booked. Peaked through the window and the place was empty so I was skeptical. I walked in and met Nelson. He exceeded my expectation! If you bring him a picture of a design, he can do it. Apparently I had walked in at just the right time because by the time I was done, he'd already had a line of people. Now I know why.This is my new spot for sure!
